==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Komtok
<hw>Kom"tok</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
African freshwater fish (<spn>Protopterus annectens</spn>), belonging to
the Dipnoi. It can breathe air by means of its lungs, and when waters
dry up, it encases itself in a nest of hard mud, where it remains till
the rainy season. It is used as food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

